---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<div id="instructions" class="mx-45 mb-40 text-gray-800 scroll-mt-25">
    <span class="text-5xl font-bold flex flex-col items-center">How to use PostureCorrector</span>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
        <ul class="text-xl mt-20 space-y-4">
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">1.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4">
                    When asked for permissions, select "allow" for both: the permission
                    to use your webcam and the permission to send desktop notifications.
                    If your browser does not ask for permissions, go to the settings and set them to "allow".
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">2.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4">
                    Select your webcam. Whenever you select a new webcam, make sure the extension
                    is turned off.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">3.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4">
                    Select your activity type. You can re-select your activity anytime you want.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">4.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4">
                    Click on the toggle button to turn on the extension. This will open a new browser 
                    tab and switch to it.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">5.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4">
                    In the new browser tab (capture page), confirm your webcam is detected and working. 
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">6.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4"> 
                    Then, click on the save button while you are sitting in your best posture. 
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">7.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4"> 
                    Don't close the browser tab (capture page) while using the extension. Also, whenever you are 
                    done, use the toggle button to turn off the extension instead of directly closing the browser tab.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-bold">8.</span>
                <span class="font-semibold pl-4"> 
                    (Optional) You can open the popup page and click on the settings icon to open the settings page
                    where you can make modify some optional settings.
                </span>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-16 w-full flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-full max-w-4xl aspect-video">
                <iframe
                    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID"
                    title="Demo Video"
                    loading="lazy"
                    class="w-full h-full rounded-xl"
                    allowfullscreen
                    allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                ></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>